---
title: Stats
---

```{r include = TRUE}
for (i in seq_along(bax_1A)){
  name = names(bax_1A[i])
  # print(shapiro.test(bax_1A[[i]]$Mean))
  if (shapiro.test(bax_1A[[i]]$Mean)$p.value >= 0.05){
    print(paste("passed :", name))
  } 
  else {print(paste("NOT passed :", name))}
}
```
